Package org.ejbca.ui.web.admin.cainterface

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminCertReqServlet
    This is a servlet that is used for creating a user into EJBCA and retrieving her certificate.
    BaseAdminServlet
    Base servlet class for all AdminWeb pages that require authentication.
    CAActivationMBean
    JSF Managed Bean or the CA Activation page of the Admin GUI.
    CACertReqServlet
    Servlet used to handle certificate requests between CAs.
    The servlet is called with method GET or POST and syntax cmd=<command>.
    CACertServlet
    Servlet used to distribute CA certificates
    cacert - returns ca certificate in PEM-format nscacert - returns ca certificate for Firefox iecacert - returns ca certificate for Internet Explorer cacert, nscacert and iecacert also takes optional parameter level=<int 1,2,...>, where the level is which ca certificate in a hierachy should be returned.
    CADataHandler
    A class help administrating CAs.
    CAExportServlet
    This Servlet exports a CA as an octet/stream.
    CAInfoView
    A class representing a view of a CA Information view..
    CAInterfaceBean
    A class used as an interface between CA jsp pages and CA ejbca functions.
    EditPublisherJSPHelper
    Contains help methods used to parse a publisher jsp page requests.
    EndEntityCertServlet
    Servlet used to distribute End Entity certificates through the "View Certificate" jsp page.
    GetCRLServlet
    Servlet used to distribute CRLs.
    The servlet is called with method GET or POST and syntax command=<command>.
    PublisherDataHandler Deprecated.
    since 6.12.0.
    ViewCAInfoJSPHelper
    Contains help methods used to parse a viewcainfo jsp page requests.
